298
00:11:30,446 --> 00:11:32,381
-So women we can
stay out of it!

299
00:11:32,414 --> 00:11:33,215
-What?

300
00:11:33,248 --> 00:11:34,183
How dare you.

301
00:11:34,316 --> 00:11:36,585
