317
00:12:09,084 --> 00:12:10,152
-Just watch, Dad.

318
00:12:10,185 --> 00:12:11,987
Ryoma can do amazing things.

319
00:12:14,523 --> 00:12:17,292
-Right hand.

320
00:12:17,326 --> 00:12:19,027
-There you go!

321
00:12:19,027 --> 00:12:20,429
Those are good hit, kid.

322
00:12:20,462 --> 00:12:22,431
