340
00:13:13,982 --> 00:13:14,650
Not bad.

341
00:13:14,883 --> 00:13:16,018
-This world's not that easy.

342
00:13:18,587 --> 00:13:19,955
Love, 15, kid.

343
00:13:23,392 --> 00:13:25,961
-All right! Way to go Dad.

