to return that ball.

352
00:13:53,155 --> 00:13:54,022
-There, Love-30.

353
00:13:57,492 --> 00:13:59,328
-What's going on with him?

354
00:13:59,361 --> 00:14:02,164
- They call him the retriever.

355
00:14:02,164 --> 00:14:03,265
The retriever?

356
00:14:03,599 --> 00:14:06,935
-Hahaha

357
00:14:06,969 --> 00:14:08,904
Ok, kid... let's see if you
can get past this test.

358
00:14:11,573 --> 00:14:13,575
