375
00:14:49,311 --> 00:14:51,146
Did he say golden?

376
00:14:51,179 --> 00:14:52,447
-Retriever?

377
00:14:55,617 --> 00:14:56,952
He's golden alright.

378
00:14:58,387 --> 00:15:01,023
