the balls that are hit.

383
00:15:15,304 --> 00:15:18,573
-There's something
strange about Ryoma.

384
00:15:18,573 --> 00:15:19,441
-What?

385
00:15:19,474 --> 00:15:20,642
-Ryoma has the serve.

386
00:15:20,876 --> 00:15:22,411
He could use his
kick serve to ace it.

387
00:15:22,444 --> 00:15:25,981
But for some reason,
he's just not using it.

388
00:15:26,014 --> 00:15:27,349
I don't understand why?

389
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:34,189
-He's going to the net.

390
00:15:34,222 --> 00:15:37,125
